Erica Ann Ginneti, 35, has been sentenced to 30 days in jail, house arrest and probation for having sex with a 17-year-old student . 
  The married mother of three from Philadelphia pleaded guilty in December to institutional sexual assault and disseminating sexually explicit materials to a minor . 
  The former math and calculus teacher had been facing seven to 14 years in prison . 
  She met her victim at the senior prom in May 2013 and the two had sex in her car in July 2013 . 
  Judge Garrett Page sentenced her to 3-23 months in jail and 60 days on house arrest . 
  She will have to perform community service and register as a sex offender . 
 